Paper: hep-th/9601065

Date: 1996-01-12

Title: Pseudoclassical supersymmetrical model for 2+1 Dirac particle

Authors: D.M. Gitman, A.E. Gon\c calves, I.V. Tyutin

Comments: 9 pages, LaTex (RevTex)

A new pseudoclassical supersymmetrical model of a spinning particle in $2+1$dimensions is proposed. Different ways of its quantization are discussed. Theyall reproduce the minimal quantum theory of the particle.